Scorers: CSL McQuaid and LJ Schierhout
12th men: CS Martin (NZ) and Imran Nazir (Pak)
4th wicket partnership (Fleming/McMillan): 50 in 52 minutes, off 60 balls
6th wicket partnership (Oram/Vincent): 50 in 44 minutes, off 65 balls
2nd wicket partnership (Saeed Anwar/Abdur Razzaq): 50 in 72 minutes, off 119 balls
4th wicket partnership (Inzamam-ul-Haq/Yousuf Youhana): 50 in 38 minutes, 65 balls
1st wicket (Saeed Anwar/Imran Farhat): 16 in 17 minutes, off 25 balls;
2nd wicket (Saeed Anwar/Abdur Razzaq): 62 in 90 minutes, off 145 balls;
3rd wicket (Abdur Razzaq/Inzamam-ul-Haq): 7 in 7 minutes, off 8 balls;
4th wicket (Inzamam-ul-Haq/Yousuf Youhana): 58 in 49 minutes, off 87 balls;
5th wicket (Yousuf Youhana/Shahid Afridi): 7* in 5 minutes, off 8 balls.
